    <measure>Proportion of participants with post-transplant virologic response</measure>
    <time_frame>Posttreatment Week 12</time_frame>
    <safety_issue>No</safety_issue>
    <description>For those participants who have a liver transplant while on study, the proportion of participants with post-transplant virologic response (PTVR, defined as HCV RNA &lt; LLOQ at 12 weeks post-transplant) will be summarized for participants in the Full Analysis Set (FAS) who have HCV RNA &lt; LLOQ at their last observed HCV RNA prior to transplant.</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
